{"name":"Dire Lemming","size":"small","type":"Beast","tag":"","alignment":"unaligned","hitDice":"2","armorName":"none","shieldBonus":0,"natArmorBonus":3,"otherArmorDesc":"12","speed":"30","burrowSpeed":"0","climbSpeed":"0","flySpeed":"0","hover":false,"swimSpeed":"0","customHP":false,"customSpeed":false,"hpText":"7 (2d6)","speedDesc":"30 ft.","strPoints":"7","dexPoints":"15","conPoints":"11","intPoints":"2","wisPoints":"10","chaPoints":"4","blindsight":"0","blind":false,"darkvision":"60","tremorsense":"0","truesight":"0","telepathy":0,"cr":"1/8","customCr":"1/8 (25 XP)","customProf":2,"isLegendary":false,"legendariesDescription":"The giant rat can take 3 legendary actions, choosing from the options below. Only one legendary action option can be used at a time and only at the end of another creature's turn. The giant rat regains spent legendary actions at the start of its turn.","isLair":false,"lairDescription":"When fighting inside its lair, the giant rat can invoke the ambient magic to take lair actions. On initiative count 20 (losing initiative ties), the giant rat can take one lair action to cause one of the following effects:","lairDescriptionEnd":"The giant rat can't repeat an effect until they have all been used, and it can't use the same effect two rounds in a row.","isMythic":false,"mythicDescription":"If the giant rat's mythic trait is active, it can use the options below as legendary actions for 1 hour after using {Some Ability}.","isRegional":false,"regionalDescription":"The region containing the giant rat's lair is warped by the creature's presence, which creates one or more of the following effects:","regionalDescriptionEnd":"If the giant rat dies, the first two effects fade over the course of 3d10 days.","properties":[],"abilities":[{"name":"Keen Smell","desc":"The lemming has advantage on Wisdom (Perception) checks that rely on smell."},{"name":"Pack Tactics","desc":"The lemming has advantage on an attack roll against a creature if at least one of the rat's allies is within 5 ft. of the creature and the ally isn't incapacitated."}],"actions":[{"name":"Bite","desc":"_Melee Weapon Attack:_ +4 to hit, reach 5 ft., one target. _Hit:_ 4 (1d4 + 2) piercing damage."}],"bonusActions":[],"reactions":[],"legendaries":[],"mythics":[],"lairs":[],"regionals":[],"sthrows":[],"skills":[],"damagetypes":[],"specialdamage":[],"conditions":[],"languages":[],"understandsBut":"","shortName":"","pluralName":"","doubleColumns":false,"separationPoint":1,"damage":[]}